function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	--enable spawners
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner,false)
		end
	end
	
	--disable well and return false so it doesn't activate
	--Remove the map icon object.
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idActorGizmo, true)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idMapIcon)
	return false;
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	--Stops spawners
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner,true)
		end
	end
	
	--Removes healing buff from possessed enemy
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idPossessed) then
		Hydra.RemoveBuffs(idPossessed, S_POSSESSION_POWER)
	end
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

	idPossessed = idActorSpawned
	
	--Grants enemy possession power one spawn anims are mostly done.
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorSpawned) then
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idActorSpawned, S_POSSESSION_POWER)
	end

end

function Start()

-- Well knockback and vfx.	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idWell, S_KNOCKBACK_POWER)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_KNOCKBACK_POWER, "CHEST_VFX", idWell)

end

function Start()
	--Enable Chest
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idChest) then 
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idChest, false)
	end 
	
	--Enable Well
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idWell) then
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idWell, false)
	end

	--Remove cursed VFX
	Hydra.BuffRemove(S_KNOCKBACK_POWER, "CHEST_VFX", idWell)

end
